rComments: Get his old tests- if you dont you will look like an idiot when u are not averaging a 95%.  They are identical. He will trick you on the third one by making a new one.  Final is very difficult.

Tough talking but fair(a little brash perhpas).Exams were 80% problems and 20% multiple choice/short answers.2 projects, equity and bond analysis.Projects were time consuming, get in a GOOD group ASAP.  Nice guy if you are nice to him.Exams are like his notes, pratice and you will be fine.  Try to get old exams, helps a lot as exams are similar.

Exams have many problems but there aren't any surprises.  Practice the problems from class and you should be fine.  Not a very forgiving grader but if you do have problems go see him.  He is actually there during office hours and is very helpful.
